cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper is about visual question answering and visual reasoning, which are tasks related to computer vision and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new framework for performing visual reasoning tasks, which involves designing interpretable models. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed model on a dataset, which could indicate that it belongs to cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
